 Psycho II | website = The Psycho Movies | accessdate = June 30, 2013 | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603054014/http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho2/ | archivedate = June 3, 2013 }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $34,725,000<ref name=\"pshchomovies\">{{Cite web | url = http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho2/ | title = Psycho II | website = The Psycho Movies | accessdate = June 30, 2013 | url-status = dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603054014/http://www.thepsychomovies.com/films/psycho2/ | archivedate = June 3, 2013 }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n|-\n| ''[[Psycho III]]''\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | July 2, 1986\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $8,400,000<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/57450-PSYCHO-III?sid=aafcd0f8-47d7-4096-a3ad-d7a6e27ed3fb&sr=0.11734072&cp=1&pos=4|title=AFI&#124;Catalog|website=catalog.afi.com}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $14,481,606<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://catalog.afi.com/Film/57450-PSYCHO-III?sid=aafcd0f8-47d7-4096-a3ad-d7a6e27ed3fb&sr=0.11734072&cp=1&pos=4|title=AFI&#124;Catalog|website=catalog.afi.com}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n|-\n| ''[[Bates Motel (film)|Bates Motel]]''\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | July 5, 1987\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n| colspan=\"3\" |  {{Hs|$0}}\u2014 Television film \u2014\n|-\n| ''[[Psycho IV: The Beginning]]''\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | November 10, 1990\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| TBA\n| colspan=\"3\" |  {{Hs|$0}}\u2014 Television film \u2014\n|-\n| ''[[Psycho (1998 film)|Psycho]]''\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | December 4, 1998\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $60,000,000<ref name=\"mojo\">{{mojo title|id=psycho98|title=Psycho (1998)}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| $21,485,655<ref name=\"mojo\">{{mojo title|id=psycho98|title=Psycho (1998)}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-alig