ed States\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 4\u20131\n| Shane Kruchten\n| Submission (armbar)\n| Dangerzone 34: Fight Farm\n| {{dts|2007|June|2}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| N/A\n| [[Waterloo, Iowa]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| align=center| 3\u20131\n| Danny Ruiz\n| Submission (armbar)\n| RFS 8: Invasion of the Cage\n| {{dts|2007|February|24}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 1:49\n| [[Tampa, Florida]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 3\u20130\n| Jason Zazelenchuk\n| Submission (rear-naked choke)\n| [[List of KOTC events|KOTC: Detonator]]\n| {{dts|2006|September|29}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 2:48\n| [[Calgary, Alberta]], Canada\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 2\u20130\n| Micah Bender\n| TKO (punches)\n| FF 3: Fightfest 3\n| {{dts|2006|May|6}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 0:31\n| [[Youngstown, Ohio]], United States\n| \n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| align=center| 1\u20130\n| Cliff Perillo\n| Submission (punches)\n| UFS: Ultimate Fight Series\n| {{dts|2006|April|15}}\n| align=center| 1\n| align=center| 1:31\n| [[Auburn, Indiana]], United States\n| \n{{end}}\n\n===Mixed martial arts exhibition record===\n{{MMA exhibition record box\n|ko-wins=0\n|ko-losses=1\n|sub-wins=1\n|sub-losses=0\n|dec-wins=0\n|dec-losses=0\n}}\n{| style=\"font-size: 85%; text-align: left;\" class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n| align=\"center\" style=\"border-style:none none solid solid; background:#f0f0f0;\"|'''Result'''\n| align=\"center\" style=\"border-style:none none solid solid; background:#f0f0f0;\"|'''Record'''\n| align=\"center\" style=\"border-style:none none solid solid; background:#f0f0f0;\"|'''Opponent'''\n| align=\"center\" style=\"border-style:none none solid solid; background:#f0f0f0;\"|'''Method'''\n| align=\"center\" style=\"border-style:none none solid solid; background:#f0f0f0;\"|'''Event'''\n| align=\"center\" style=\"border-style:none none solid solid; background:#f0f0f0;\"|'''Date'''\n| align